         data-de="<strong>Viven AG</strong><br>Film- &amp; Videoproduktion<br>Zeughausstrasse 31<br>8004 Zürich<br>Schweiz"
         data-es="<strong>Viven AG</strong><br>Producción de cine y video<br>Zeughausstrasse 31<br>8004 Zúrich<br>Suiza"><strong>Viven AG</strong><br>Film &amp; Video Production<br>Zeughausstrasse 31<br>8004 Zürich<br>Switzerland</p>

      <h3 data-en="Represented by" data-de="Vertreten durch" data-es="Representada por">Represented by</h3>
      <p data-en="Sebastian Cepeda, Managing Director"
         data-de="Sebastian Cepeda, Geschäftsführer"
         data-es="Sebastian Cepeda, Director General">Sebastian Cepeda, Managing Director</p>

      <h3 data-en="Contact" data-de="Kontakt" data-es="Contacto">Contact</h3>
      <p data-en='Phone: <a href="tel:+41435083381">+41 43 508 33 81</a><br>Email: <a href="mailto:info@viven.ch">info@viven.ch</a>'
         data-de='Telefon: <a href="tel:+41435083381">+41 43 508 33 81</a><br>E-Mail: <a href="mailto:info@viven.ch">info@viven.ch</a>'
         data-es='Teléfono: <a href="tel:+41435083381">+41 43 508 33 81</a><br>Correo electrónico: <a href="mailto:info@viven.ch">info@viven.ch</a>'>Phone: <a href="tel:+41435083381">+41 43 508 33 81</a><br>Email: <a href="mailto:info@viven.ch">info@viven.ch</a></p>

      <h3 data-en="Commercial register &amp; VAT" data-de="Handelsregister &amp; MWST" data-es="Registro mercantil e IVA">Commercial register &amp; VAT</h3>
      <p data-en="Viven AG is registered in the Swiss Commercial Register.<br>VAT / UID number: CHE-266.556.186 MWST"
         data-de="Die Viven AG ist im Schweizer Handelsregister eingetragen.<br>MWST- / UID-Nummer: CHE-266.556.186 MWST"
         data-es="Viven AG está inscrita en el Registro Mercantil suizo.<br>Número de IVA / UID: CHE-266.556.186 MWST">Viven AG is registered in the Swiss Commercial Register.<br>VAT / UID number: CHE-266.556.186 MWST</p>

